snippet.title: Demolish & Build 3 - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
💥 IT'S OFFICIAL! 💥
Meet Demolish & Build 3, a new sequel to the popular series! 🏗
👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203670
New in-game features include:
Realistic destruction model - every fragment is physically simulated. 
Company management - build an empire with multiple vehicle parks and offices. 
Variety of vehicles - with detailed models and sounds. 

#demolishandbuild3 #game
